# Fundraiser CLI application

This is a simple CLI application for managing donations to charities. You can add, edit, view, and delete charities, as well as record donations. You can also import charities from a CSV file.

## Features

- View a list of charities
- Add a new charity
- Edit an existing charity
- Delete a charity
- Add a donation
- Import charities from a CSV file

## Requirements

- **PHP**: Application has been created on PHP 8.3 version

## Installation

1. **Download the project**

   git clone https://github.com/ignaspu/Fundraiser-App.git
   cd Fundraiser-App
   php src/cli.php